txt.en: 'It is a worthwhile trade! I am glad you agree. This is all I have though. Perhaps I will acquire more Embers soon!'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Completing this quest will remove 100 Umbari Tâm.</rgb>
The citizens of Umbar Baharbêl have a small quantity of Embers available.
'If you are looking for Embers, I have just a few. I would be willing to part with them if you have some Umbari Tâm.'\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Collect 100 Umbari Tâm to trade with the Umbar Quartermaster.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Talk to the Umbar Quartermaster to trade Umbari Tâm for Embers.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This quest can be completed weekly.</rgb>
Deliver the Umbari Tâm to the Umbar Quartermaster
